data.meta_description: View the 2020 school ranking data, year 12 VCE student rankings and VCE subject data for Ringwood Secondary College Vic, as well as ranking comparison charts, trends over time, plus other noteable awards won by students at the school.
data.text:
School Statistics Charts

To view the statistics and trends for Ringwood Secondary College on the chart below, select one or more items from the dropdown list.

Multiple data items can be selected in any combination. Up to seven years of data is displayed.

Measurements and #rankings are displayed against the left axis. Percentages(%) are displayed against the right axis.

School Ranking Ladders

Below are the 2020 VCE school ranking ladders.

The first ladder below shows the position of Ringwood Secondary College when all schools are ranked by their 2020 median VCE study scores (as published by the VCAA). If two schools have equal median scores, their VCE 40+ percentages are used as a tie-breaker.

The second ladder below shows the position of Ringwood Secondary College when all schools are ranked by their 2020 VCE 40+ percentage measures, (as published by the VCAA). If two schools have equal 40+ percentages, their 40+ score counts are used as a tie-breaker.

Ranking positions are assigned to the top 400 schools.
